<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="system-bar">
    <div>
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        <span>SISTEMA OPERATIVO</span>
        &nbsp;|&nbsp;
        <span>LegacyReportEngine/2.1.3</span>
    </div>
    <div class="system-bar-right">
        <span id="sys-clock" class="text-mono">00:00:00</span>
    </div>
</div>

<nav class="main-nav">
    <a href="/" class="nav-brand">
        <div class="nav-brand-icon">LR</div>
        <div>
            <div class="nav-brand-text">LegacyReport</div>
            <span class="nav-brand-version">v2.1.3</span>
        </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/"        class="nav-link">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/reports" class="nav-link">Import XML</a>
    <a href="/login"   class="nav-link active">Accesso</a>
</nav>

<div class="page-wrapper" style="max-width:760px">

    <div class="page-header">
        <div>
            <div class="page-label">// Autenticazione completata</div>
            <h1 class="page-title">Token emesso</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">Benvenuto, <strong><%= username %></strong>. Conserva il token per le richieste successive.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="badge badge-green">AUTH OK</span>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-success">
        <span class="alert-prefix">[OK]</span>
        <span>JWT RS256 generato con successo. Valido per 2 ore.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <span class="card-header-title">Bearer Token</span>
            <button class="copy-btn" data-copy="token-value">COPIA</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body" style="padding:0">
            <div class="token-box" id="token-value"><%= token %></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mt-24">
        <div class="card-header">
            <span class="card-header-title">Come utilizzare il token</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-dim" style="font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; margin-bottom:16px">
                Includere il token nell'header di ogni richiesta autenticata:
            </p>
            <div class="terminal">Authorization: Bearer <span style="color:var(--accent-amber)"><%= token.substring(0,40) %>...</span></div>
            <hr class="divider">
            <p class="text-dim" style="font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px">
                Il token contiene i tuoi claims: <strong style="color:var(--text-secondary)">user: <%= username %>, role: user</strong><br>
                Algoritmo di firma: <strong style="color:var(--text-secondary)">RS256</strong><br>
                Chiave pubblica di verifica: <a href="/.well-known/jwks.json" style="color:var(--accent-green)">/.well-known/jwks.json</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 flex gap-8">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">← Dashboard</a>
        <a href="/reports" class="btn btn-primary">Importa Report</a>
    </div>

</div>

<footer class="main-footer">
    <span>LegacyReportEngine v2.1.3 &copy; 2024 Legacy Corp.</span>
    <span>Apache/2.2.31 (Ubuntu)</span>
</footer>

<script src="/js/dashboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
